#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_noisetexture.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`OpenSimplexNoise <class_OpenSimplexNoise>` filled texture."
msgstr ":ref:`OpenSimplexNoise <class_OpenSimplexNoise>` 填充的纹理。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_noisetexture.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_noisetexture.rst:19
msgid ""
"Uses an :ref:`OpenSimplexNoise <class_OpenSimplexNoise>` to fill the "
"texture data. You can specify the texture size but keep in mind that "
"larger textures will take longer to generate and seamless noise only "
"works with square sized textures."
msgstr ""
"使用一个 :ref:`OpenSimplexNoise <class_OpenSimplexNoise>` "
"来填充纹理数据。您可以指定纹理大小，但要记住，较大的纹理将花费更长的时间来生成，而无缝噪声仅适用于方形纹理。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_noisetexture.rst:21
msgid "NoiseTexture can also generate normalmap textures."
msgstr "噪波纹理还可以生成法线贴图。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_noisetexture.rst:23
msgid ""
"The class uses :ref:`Thread <class_Thread>`\\ s to generate the texture "
"data internally, so :ref:`Texture2D.get_data "
"<class_Texture2D_method_get_data>` may return ``null`` if the generation "
"process has not completed yet. In that case, you need to wait for the "
"texture to be generated before accessing the data:"
msgstr ""

